creator: Truliant Federal Credit Union
descriptionHtml:
Tru2Go for Android allows you to access your accounts, transfer funds, pay bills, view and activate your cash back offers and even deposit checks* with your Android device. We also offer a convenient ATM and Member Financial Center locator tool.

DO YOU HAVE A SUBSCRIPTION FEE?
No, it’s FREE**. We are pleased to offer our Tru2Go app with no monthly subscription fee for use of this product to our member-owners. Easy Deposit is free for depositing up to 25 checks each month***.

For additional information about the Tru2Go apps, please refer to our Mobile Banking page at www.TruliantFCU.org.

* Easy Pay Bill Payment and Easy Deposit are subject to approval.
** Your carrier may charge data access fees. Please check with your carrier or review your mobile phone contract for additional details.
*** Easy Deposit is free for up to 25 checks/month. For each month you deposit 26 checks or more you will be a charged $25/month.

To learn how we protect your privacy, please visit https://www.truliantfcu.org/Privacy-Policy

creator: TRULIANT FEDERAL CREDIT UNION
descriptionHtml:
Truliant’s mobile banking app puts your finances at your fingertips.



Effortless Account Management: Check balances, transfer funds, and deposit checks anytime, anywhere - ditch the branch visits!
Convenience is King: Open new accounts and apply for loans in minutes.
Bill Pay: Schedule payments, say goodbye to late fees, and keep your budget on track.
Loan Management Made Easy: Pay down your loans with ease and even apply for new ones - all within the app.
Security You Can Trust: Robust security measures to keep your finances safe, so you can bank with peace of mind.



For more details and to learn about Truliant's commitment to your privacy, visit:


Digital Banking Page: https://www.truliantfcuonline.org/tob/live/usp-core/app/login/consumer
Security & Privacy: https://www.truliantfcu.org/security-center/privacy-policy
